column5: Anyone interested in mussel hunting... http://wimp.com/racetide/
Jeez, I felt claustrophobic just watching that
Can't watch it all....just call me a chicken liver....
Ya gotta REALLY enjoy mussels to take that kind of a risk !!
And for $5 I can buy 2 pounds of them....
I don't think these fellas have a "bulk barn" around the corner lads!
Thats Awesome !!!... I just love those David Attenborough films - got the whole "planet earth" series last year... dont think I have ever seen that one before though.
anyone know where id be able to stream full episodes online of this show?
Thanks in advance for tonight's nightmare Billy Bob!

5 gal bucket /  several  tose guys are nuts.!!!
So next time you have a bad day of fishing, think of these guys when they have a BAD DAY...
